@Pawel: GTK2 option was added in commit 312150 to support an experimental GTK2 UI in GeneWeb v6.06. It looks like its references in plist got removed in commit 354265, when I updated to GeneWeb v6.07 and added staging. As near as I can remember, I think it didn't look like the experimental GTK2 UI was included in the distribution anymore (hence its removal from the plist), however I left the option in place in case it would resurface in a later revision.

I am OK with the removal of the GTK2 option.

@Kubilay: I uploaded the attachments externally because I was used to the old PR system not being able to handle large diffs. I'll try to remember to upload directly into Bugzilla.

Regarding splitting this diff, I can do it, but if it's really not necessary, then I'd be happier to avoid the extra work. I'll wait to hear back on this.
